"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8678178-a-fresh-start-the-key-to-aussie-bruces-olympic-dreams\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weightlifting wasn't quite the sport Kyle Bruce had in mind when he grew up dreaming of the Olympics, instead wanting to play for the Wallabies.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"score\": 0.9999746338469248, \"rank\": 2.5288235110509497e-05, \"text\": \"Kyle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  But the dream changed when his rugby-loving father died in 2015, and weightlifting became a necessary fresh start for the 24-year-old.\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Years of self-funded training and working two nights a week at a pizza joint during school paid off in the end for Bruce, who is gearing up for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am grateful to be here, to make the Olympics.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's any Australian kid's dream,\\\" he told AAP.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9991427627703178, \"rank\": 0.0008578314864434594, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A piece of his father remains close to him nevertheless, donning his dad's compression shirt at every competition - and Paris will not be the exception.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995475264, \"rank\": 4.524815117139218e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He'd be proud, for sure.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up, sport was a massive thing in my family,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bruce's mum Alison was in tears after he was named in the announcement on June 2.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8155250467444443e-14, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She cries all the time.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very hesitant to bring her,\\\" he said, laughing.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weightlifter thought he'd struck gold when he made his Commonwealth Games debut in Birmingham in 2022, but judges denied him the medal when a review showed his arms had not fully extended.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9999988377114666, \"rank\": 9.670642874926004e-07, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has had two years to reflect on that one moment being taken away, which he reckons was a lesson in disguise.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In hindsight, it was the best thing that could have happened to me.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a bit of an ego going into (Birmingham), expecting a lot more,\\\" Bruce said.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9999988377114666, \"rank\": 9.670642874926004e-07, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want that to happen again.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to go in there with execution, and do the best we can - make sure those little things are crisp.\\\"\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition this year is fierce and filled with hungry eyes, with 60 men and women competing in each of the 10 weight classes - all scrambling for gold.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bruce, in the men's 89kg class, is just one of three 24-year-old weightlifters representing the nation at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's joined by Eileen Cikamatana in the women's 81kg division, and Jacqui Nichele in the women's 71kg.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Cikamatana\", \"score\": 0.9999980875591161, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eileen Cikamatana\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Cikamatana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Cikamatana\"}, {\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\", \"score\": 0.9999999903807293, \"rank\": 9.61916795797245e-09, \"text\": \"Jacqui\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia has had no Olympic medals in the sport since 1996, but Bruce is prepared to raise the bar.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999821368982557, \"rank\": 1.1872078892954033e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously Eileen is the big medal contender ... with her efforts and results,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But in saying that, do not count out Jacqui and myself ... anything can happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\", \"score\": 0.9999999903807293, \"rank\": 9.61916795797245e-09, \"text\": \"Jacqui\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_McQueen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The weightlifting competitions are scheduled to run between August 7-11 at France's largest exhibition centre, Paris Expo Porte de Versailles.\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2601, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9781942569479241, \"rank\": 0.020544578184302813, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Associated Press  Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also includes evening update.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it happens  Do not miss updates on news about the Public Service.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Catch up on the news of the day and unwind with great reading for your evening.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Get the editor's insights: what's happening & why it matters.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice weekly  Stay in the know on news that matters to you with twice weekly newsletters from The Senior.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Going out or staying in?\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Find out what's on.\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daily  The latest news, results & expert analysis.\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daily  Your exclusive preview of David Pope's latest cartoon.\", \"from\": 3319, \"